high_descs: walk to face right side of kitchen table
pick up white mug from table
heat mug in microwave, remove mug from microwave
gaze upward to cabinet above microwave
anns.task_desc: put heated mug into a cabinet

high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn right and walk to the counter then step to your left and walk one step forward then turn right.
Pick up the mug that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the counter in front of you then turn right.
Warm the mug in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Look up at the cupboard above the microwave.
Open the cupboard above the sink and put the mug to the left of the clear bowl before closing the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm mug in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn right to face the counter in the middle of the room
Pick up the coffee cup from the counter
Turn right and go to the microwave by the refrigerator
Open the microwave door, put the mug in the microwave and close the door. Turn on the microwave and then open the door and take out the cup
Look to the cabinets above the microwave
Open the cabinet door, put the mug to the left of the bowl and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved coffee mug in a cabinet
